The most recent family diagnosis for the 
<taxonomicName box="[749,886,222,246]" class="Malacostraca" family="Epimeriidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Epimeriidae</taxonomicName>
is that of 
<bibRefCitation author="Coleman" box="[1005,1323,222,246]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" refString="Coleman, C. O. &amp; Barnard, J. L. (1991) Revision of Iphimediidae and similar families (Amphipoda: Gammaridea). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington., 104, 253 - 268." type="journal article" year="1991">
Coleman &amp; Barnard (
<number box="[1253,1313,222,246]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" value="1991.0">1991</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Coleman" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" refString="Coleman, C. O. (2007) Synopsis of the Amphipoda of the Southern Ocean; Volume 2: Acanthonotozomellidae, Amathillopsidae, Dikwidae, Epimeriidae, Iphimediidae, Ochlesidae and Vicmusiidae. Bulletin de l'institut Royal des Sciences Naturelles de Belgique. Biologie, 77, Supplement 2, 1 - 142." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Coleman (
<number box="[159,218,258,282]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" value="2007.0">2007</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
provided a key to the 
<collectingCountry box="[489,593,258,282]" name="Antarctica" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">Antarctic</collectingCountry>
species of 
<taxonomicName box="[725,866,258,282]" class="Malacostraca" family="Epimeriidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Epimeriidae</taxonomicName>
. A summary of Pacific 
<taxonomicName box="[1141,1281,258,282]" class="Malacostraca" family="Epimeriidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Epimeriidae</taxonomicName>
, including an identification key, was published by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lorz" box="[561,697,294,318]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" refString="Lorz, A. N. (2011) Pacific Epimeriidae (Amphipoda: Crustacea): Epimeria. Journal of the Marine Biological Association of the United Kingdom 91, 471 - 477" type="journal article" year="2011">
Lörz (
<number box="[629,689,294,318]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" value="2011.0">2011</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
